'''Curtas Vila do Conde''' International Film Festival, created in 1993, is one of the most important cinematographic and cultural events in Portugal dedicated to short-films and annually produced in July, in the city [[Vila do Conde]]. The edition of 2011 had more than 20 000 spectators.<ref>http://www.publico.pt/Cultura/curtas-vila-do-conde-volta-a-ter-mais-de-20-mil-espectadores-1503593</ref> In 2012 the festival celebrates the 20th Edition.<ref>http://festival.curtas.pt/festival/intro/</ref>
